Package org.globus.opensaml11.md.xml

Class Summary
Parser Obtain schema validating and non-validating XML parsers.
Parser.DOMParser A dummy class that pretends to be an old Xerces DOMParser to simplify conversion of existing code.
SchemasDirectoryImpl Find Schemas in a Resource directory
SchemasResourceListImpl Find Schemas as a list of resource files.
SchemaStore Compile a Schema object from a Map of DOM objects representing XSD files keyed by the Namespace that the XSD defines.
